Title: Female-Condom Use in a Gender-Specific Family Planning Clinic Trial
Journal: American Journal of Public Health
Author-Name: Hoffman, S.
Author-Name: Exner, T.M.
Author-Name: Leu, C.-S.
Author-Name: Ehrhardt, A.A.
Author-Name: Stein, Z.
Year: 2003
Volume: 93
Issue: 11
